;">measured value</span></span><span class=3D"mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span cla=
ss=3D"mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style=3D"padding-top: 0.298em; padding-bott=
om: 0.446em;">=E2=88=92</span></span><span class=3D"mjx-mtext MJXc-space2">=
<span class=3D"mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style=3D"padding-top: 0.372em; pad=
ding-bottom: 0.372em;">actual value</span></span></span></span></span></spa=
n></p>

<p>Suppose we have a distance of <span class=3D"mjpage"><span class=3D"mjx-=
chtml"><span class=3D"mjx-math" aria-label=3D"500\text{ feet}"><span class=
=3D"mjx-mrow" aria-hidden=3D"true"><span class=3D"mjx-mn"><span class=3D"mj=
